title: Did the British police find Putin's passport at the scene of the Salisbury Sam attack?
subtitle: A naive website received accusations of Putin ' s involvement in poisoning in March 2018 of a former Russian spy on British soil to the fullest extent.

vclaim: The British police found the passport of Russian President Vladimir Putin at the scene of a chemical attack on a former Russian spy, Sergei Skripal, in Salsbury, England.
